                            <comment id="17394550" author="davsclaus" created="Fri, 6 Aug 2021 06:33:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;camel-main is intended for microservices styles where you dont dynamic add new routes and so on. But what we can tie this to is whether lightweight is true or false, so if false, then dont clear, if true then clear. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17394560" author="davsclaus" created="Fri, 6 Aug 2021 06:46:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So with the lightweight mode then this is actually better, as adding dyanamic routes is not allowed there so you get a better error&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
